Although I am pretty pleased with the program the way it is now,
here are some improvements that I may decide to implement:

  · More video codecs
  · PPC support


And here are some suggestions from other people which might or
might not get implemented.  I'm just listing them here so that
you don't have to suggest them too...  :)

  · Providing a Datatype as well
